    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-cvsl-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation levels for Model Risk Level 2. The six not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. The CFD model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump in the CPB application. This assessment was conducted under the Minimal profile; a subsequent Complete-profile submission will provide a structured Context of Use binding.",
